Beer spending was highest for NCR at P2.1 billion (28%), followed by North Luzon and Visayas at P1.4 billion (20%) and P1.5 billion (20%), respectively.
Mindanao posted P1.3 billion (18%), then South Luzon with P1 billion (14%).
