CFA databank and research Another development in the water industry is water delivery through mobile water tanks.
Under this scheme, 30 drum capacity tanks mounted on trucks deliver water for all-purpose use to homes and small business establishments.
Orders are taken by the drum (40 gal/drum) which cost P20-25 per drum in Baguio City and P30 per drum in Metro Manila.
