Import Inspection and Clearance of Consignment from Canada 1.
Registration of Application The importer or his agent shall file an application in PQ Form-15 in triplicate in respect of each cargo immediately upon arrival or in advance in case of perishable consignments to the officer-in-charge of plant quarantine station at the notified point of entry along with following enclosures:
