Intensive marketing by Snapple (owned by Cadbury-Schweppes) has certainly helped breathe new life into this segment.
In response to this initiative, the big beverage makers have formed partnerships with the best-known brands in the field, and have thus been able to rapidly develop new products and grab a large share of the market.
