Swiss Exhibition (Messe Schweiz) promoting IGEHO Instead of launching Lefa (Trade fair for the food wholesale and retail trade), Swiss Exhibition will be expanding Igeho (the International Exhibition for Industrial and Institutional Catering, Hotels and Restaurants).
From now on, Igeho will be showcasing all segments of the out-of-home market.
